<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 0 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:

- Copy


First day of week and month, I wish to start all the things which i planned.
Filled the office time sheets. Planned for 1 hr. It took 2 hrs to complete, In the first half gone quickly.
After the lunch, Check about the file and content organising about the obsidian tutorials. Seen very curiously to implement and continue this practice for the long term.
Evening gone for break, Me, Sajja, Swetha talks about the appraisal and company growth and self growth.
Evening received the HIKVision camera and External hard disk case, Gave the case to attach the HDD.
Back to home try to attach the camera in Desktop, In linux it is not compatible.

#MyInsights

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 2 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:


#MyInsights: Understand the importance of organising the work
Explored, How to organise the folder structure management efficiently. It is not the one time setup. It is the fine tuning process.



Booked the train tickets to goto madurai on September 4, October 4, October 25.
Today organised the all the bank statements, and credit card transaction details.
No work in office.
Evening Karthick marketing came in evening and discussed regarding the E-Commerce website. Made the call with Mano. Need to say the quote amount tomorrow.
Spoke to manoj about the dissatisfaction regarding the appraisal.
Came to home spoke to Aarthy, Avva. And Spoke to mom, She told no power since the morning. Need to make the UPS in home. Adding this item in the bucket list.

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 7 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:

Its a peaceful day, Got wakes up on 7 AM. Had the raagi in home. Went office with very casual day. Not the office work weightage day.
Continues today folder split up. cleared and organised files.
Spoke to LIC Thangaraj, He told return the document next visit.
Quote the 40k Amount for the e-commerce project and spoke john impulse.

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 8 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:


1
2
3


Continued the file organisation in mac and google drive.
Feeling so relax, have the happy mindset to made all things easier.
Evening Me, Aadhu, Preethi went to open market bought the toys Ganesh's son and daughter, purchased vegetables. Planing this Sunday to go their home.
From today Preethi's home management task started. She agreed all the expenses will take by her. She only paid for toys and vegetables.
For the dinner bought the Briyani and chicken fry due to late get back home.

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 7 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:


Realised how i missed showcase of my work.
Am happy what done in the last one year. But the rewards i missed. In future need to give focus into it.


Organised the all the bank statements, Spoke to the Citi bank customer and requested to get all the month credit card statements. From this month to Axis bank undertaking the Citi bank. So that it help for the future references.
Evening spoke to Siva PSS, spoke about appraisal and disappointment of the present situation. He explained the all the situations. Helps me to understands the all the perspective.
Understands how to showcase the works.

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 7 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:





Today mostly completed the file organisation works.
In the second half, Started to create the Github repo and synced with the already created projects
In the evening went to rama temple, met vijay anna and their family. They came to home to us, because vijay's mom tomorrow planning to go hometown.
In the meanwhile we planned to go Balaji Creation shop to purchase cloths for the Ganesh kids.
We purchased cloths for the ganesh kids and Amizh too.
After the purchase had the momos, mysore masal dosa and for the dinner had the parotta.
Very pleasant day.

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 7 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:





Woke-up around 8'o clock. Made the call to mom while walking.
I prepared the curd rice in the morning, from the yesterday remaining rice.
Gone for saloon to adjust the beard, Preethi scold me on that time.
Got the sweets from Rajasthan sweets Half Kg milk sweet Rs280 and Mixure Rs150.
Got delay to get cabs tried on ola, uber and finally got the booking in rapido.
Asked about the Auto driver regarding land investment, he told make the investment in medimallasandra location. Need to check this. Gave the amount
Reached their home around 1 30 PM
Spend the nice time with Ganesh family. Very nice lunch(Chicken briyani, Mutton gravy, Egg). Awesome.
Discussed on so many talks. Vani attai told think about the home construction, Before Aadhu grows.
Finally they gifted dresses for me and preethi along with Rs500. Precious moment. For Aarthy also I need to give the treat, she told.
Started around 6:30 PM through rapido, Reached home around 7:30 PM. That hosakote road is good i felt and told same to preethi.
In the night spoke to dad, mom, Subburaj mama, atthai and aarthy over the phone.
Video call with bhava and aarthy so happy day, Felt like life got balanced to met these kind of gatherings.

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 8 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:


Received the 2024 Appraisal letter.
This is the day1 of my journal begins


Wakes at 8 AM.
Explored about the obsidian tutorials
Learnt organise the habits
After receiving the appraisal letter, felt bad about the numbers which i seen, Happens at 6 PM
Decided to keep doing the things consistently with self satisfaction
Yesterday gave the advance amount to #Amrudha jewellers(1.6 L), Before day (27, June 2024) gave the amount 40K.
Evening shown the increment letter Preethi and Aadhavan. This is the special letter after the Aadhu's birth. I gave the letter to him first. Preethi gets happy.

#T20Wordcup-2024

<< Yesterday | Tomorrow >>
Sleeping 7 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:


#T20Wordcup-2024 final today IND vs SA
Ind 176-7 SA- 169- 8 India won by 7 runs
After marriage and with Aadhavan First match


Reached office late, Morning gone for cycling and thought about yesterday's appraisal letter in HAL road
Not done great today, In confusion of all the things. Tried to organise the life
Back at home 5 PM, Discussed with vijay at KA12 Tea shop, Regarding the appraisal process. After having the discussion with him got relaxed little.
Went temple today after the so long. Felt good planning to make it happen regularly.
Tomorrow Aarthy going to Udumalaipet. Subburaj mama came to home to took her tomorrow.
Preethi asked nandini milk sweet, but we can't get it. Came to home prepared Chapathi and Poori with musroom curry for the dinner. Had the Jam bread.
Spoke with video call with home. Aarthy felt like missing the family in madurai.

Sleeping 2 0 10

Habit Tracker Writing: Workout: Reading:

Its the pleasant day, Aarthy back to udumalpet with her mama.
Dad & mom went to Selvaraj naina home for asking about the eye surgery.
Preethi's Elite briyani today nailed it, Top notch.
Made the call with Parani mama, Asha ganesh, Jeeva wife preethi.
Totally different pleasant day to compare to the earlier week ends.
Me and Preethi, discussed today about where to buy the house, Shared the thought about how to execute it.
